HUMMINGBIRD GAMES PRIVACY POLICY
Last Updated: September 12, 2024
This Privacy Policy explains how HUMMINGBIRD GAMES PTE.LTD. (herein referred to as "we" or "us", our Google Developer Name is: HummingBirdGames) collects, stores, uses, or otherwise handles your personal information when you use our Services (referred to as "you"). It also details your rights regarding our processing of your personal data.
In this document, "Services" includes our Games, Websites, and any related services or properties we control. "Games" refers to our various gaming apps and products. "Websites" relates to the web pages and online platforms we oversee. When we refer to "your data," we mean personal information that identifies or can identify you.
This Privacy Policy applies to all our Services unless a specific Game or Service has its own distinct Privacy Policy, which will then take precedence. Additionally, our Services may link to or provide access to third-party properties. This Privacy Policy does not cover these third-party sites, and their operators may collect and use your data according to their own policies.
We encourage you to read this Privacy Policy thoroughly before using or accessing our Services to understand how and why we handle your data. While some sections offer brief summaries for convenience, a full read of the Privacy Policy will provide a more complete understanding. We also suggest reviewing our Terms of Service, which govern your use of our Services.
I Data controller
The term "data controller" refers to an entity that decides how and why personal data is processed. In relation to the activities described in this Privacy Policy, HUMMINGBIRD GAMES PTE.LTD., located at 3 TEMASEK AVENUE, #27-02, CENTENNIAL TOWER, SINGAPORE 039190, acts as the data controller.
While operating our Services, we may work with partners to whom we may share your data. Some of these partners function as separate data controllers, determining their own purposes and methods for processing your data. For more information about these partners and their data handling practices, please refer to section VII of this Privacy Policy.
II Contact information
For any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us by email:masong@hummingbirdgamesltd.com.
We have designated a Data Protection Officer (DPO) to oversee data protection matters. If you have any concerns or inquiries regarding the management of your data, you can reach out to our DPO via email:masong@hummingbirdgamesltd.com.
